The paper also mentions the use of the language for complex post-processing tasks, which can involve machine learning and data analysis techniques, making cs.LG a possible category. The paper also discusses the syntax and semantics of the language, which are related to software engineering and programming languages, making cs.SE a possible category. Finally, the paper presents an algorithm for validating the language, which involves formal methods and logic, making cs.PL a possible category.
